    "description": "This carb smart recipe replaces half the white rice for cauliflower rice Once your pan is hot, this easy stir-fry comes together in no time. You'll serve meat-free chick'n, sweet peppers and sweet pea pods in soy and red chilli relish, and serve with toasty sesame rice. Hao chi (delicious)!",
